title: Don't Gank Aatrox

embed.description: A short compilation of Aatrox Mid turning around ganks. Ryze and Zac get in trouble while trying to kill the sustain king Aatrox. JUST DON'T GANK HIM. Thumbnail picture made by - http://korhiper.deviantart.com/ Songs used from NCS: Song: it's different - Shadows (feat. Miss Mary) [NCS Release] Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds.

body:
Hello guys, I've made a short compilation about Aatrox, just a start will soon make some more/better content so feel free to subscribe! Also please comment/criticize me about the quality of the video (not only visual) so I can improve!
Please check it out! 
Thanks :)

replies.body:
Nice to see Aatrox getting some attention.
Cheers,
A fellow lv6 Aatrox main.
